{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "dfb82ae8-dbe8-4e51-b339-8b334947fa15", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/dfb82ae8-dbe8-4e51-b339-8b334947fa15@1.pkg/1772597705604/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597706069", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/dfb82ae8-dbe8-4e51-b339-8b334947fa15@1.pkg/1772597705604/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597706069"}, "identifier": "dfb82ae8-dbe8-4e51-b339-8b334947fa15", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查理解中学时代对人生发展的重要意义。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：&ldquo;</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>更多的是为生在伟大祖国感到骄傲、生逢伟大时代感到幸运</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>&rdquo;启示我们要珍惜伟大时代带来的美好中学时光，因此C正确。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：&ldquo;中学时代是我们三观成熟的关键期&rdquo;错误，中学时代是我们初步形成三观的关键期，而非三观成熟的关键期。A错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：并非只有成为航天员才能为祖国贡献，实现人生价值。B错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：情感体验不会随</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>年龄增长自然成熟</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>。C错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选C</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）</span><span>中国航天员王亚平在给学生的回信中写道：&ldquo;每每飞临祖国上空&hellip;&hellip;我的内心升腾起的除了震撼，更多的是为生在伟大祖国感到骄傲、生逢伟大时代感到幸运。&rdquo;她的话引发了学生的共鸣。这</span><span>启示刚刚升入初中的我们</span><span>（　　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）中国航天员王亚平在给学生的回信中写道：“每每飞临祖国上空……我的内心升腾起的除了震撼，更多的是为生在伟大祖国感到骄傲、生逢伟大时代感到幸运。”她的话引发了学生的共鸣。这启示刚刚升入初中的我们（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/dfb82ae8-dbe8-4e51-b339-8b334947fa15@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977876064", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>中学时代是</span><span>三观成熟的关键时期，是人生新起点</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>只有成为航天员才能</span><span>为祖国贡献，</span><span>实现人生价值</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>生逢伟大时代，要珍惜中学阶段的生命成长礼物</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>情感体验会随年龄增长自然成熟，无需主动培养</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）</span><span>中国航天员王亚平在给学